caller_intent: David Butler is seeking assistance with obtaining homeowner's insurance, clarifying he does not currently have a policy with Alliance Insurance but has Auto insurance with them.
resolution_steps: Agent asked if David has a policy with Alliance Insurance.
David confirmed he has Auto insurance but no homeowner's policy.
Agent offered to transfer David to an agent specializing in homeowner's insurance.
knowledge_required: Understanding of insurance product types (Auto vs. Homeowner's)
Call transfer procedures for specialty insurance lines
summary: David Butler contacted Alliance Insurance to inquire about homeowner's insurance, revealing he has Auto insurance with the agency. The agent acknowledged his Auto policy and offered to connect him with a specialist for homeowner's insurance needs.
